程序包 org.cloudbus.cloudsim.provisioners

  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    BwProvisioner
    BwProvisioner is an abstract class that represents the provisioning policy used by a host to allocate bandwidth (bw) to virtual machines inside it.
    BwProvisionerSimple
    BwProvisionerSimple is an extension of BwProvisioner which uses a best-effort policy to allocate bandwidth (bw) to VMs: if there is available bw on the host, it allocates; otherwise, it fails.
    BwProvisionerSimpleTest  
    PeProvisioner
    /** PeProvisioner is an abstract class that represents the provisioning policy used by a host to allocate its PEs to virtual machines inside it.
    PeProvisionerSimple
    PeProvisionerSimple is an extension of PeProvisioner which uses a best-effort policy to allocate virtual PEs to VMs: if there is available mips on the physical PE, it allocates to a virtual PE; otherwise, it fails.
    PeProvisionerSimpleTest  
    RamProvisioner
    RamProvisioner is an abstract class that represents the provisioning policy used by a host to allocate memory to virtual machines inside it.
    RamProvisionerSimple
    RamProvisionerSimple is an extension of RamProvisioner which uses a best-effort policy to allocate memory to VMs: if there is available ram on the host, it allocates; otherwise, it fails.
    RamProvisionerSimpleTest
